      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BOMBASTIC LOLA (2) started big odds last time but hit the ground running with a slick early split, giving a sight but fading out of it to finish fourth (19.51) at this track over 350m. Better than last start and worth following up. MIDGET EMERALD (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (20.41) in a Grade 6 at Capalaba. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Can do much better this time. HARD STYLE TIGER (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (19.95) in a Grade 6 at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. OHTANI FORCE (3) will be hard to beat with a drop in distance.",
